item.title: Adding Objects To A 718 Source
item.dc:creator: @Potzon Potzon
item.description:
@Potzon wrote:

First of all: No source has got the Client.java file, you can find it in the client folder.

If you would like to spawn an object, you have to use the unpackedSpawnsList file. You can find it in the “data\map” folder.
